{"tid":1096723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗十幾萬登頭版同個過氣廢中嘈交真係好撚有意義呀","createTime":"2019-04-08T01:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T13:32:50.000Z","uid":66260,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"086252555a68eec22b5a16d7dcfda3033b861346","tid":1096723,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"689一定會好嬲嬲豬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知佢會點回應呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FAyFYV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FAyFYV.jpg&h=bde3ac38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<code>吳文遠的搞笑廣告</code><br />\n人地一早知係你行人路大將軍搞事啦，淨係提佢個名咋<br />\n<br />\n冇啦完啦散場啦<br />\n大家打完飛機爽唔爽呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n義士繼續坐監，DQ既繼續被DQ, 逃犯條例大灣區國歌法繼續強姦香港人<br />\n屌關我撚事咩？登報串689一鑊先叫重要事呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肥佬黎咩都唔使做就有錢收，蘋果日報或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"83bb7fd4e7e12ff3e0f70fbbb9b63c932616a7db","tid":1096723,"uid":66260,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:04:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=828452537517225&amp;set=a.127929567569529&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D828452537517225%26set%3Da.127929567569529%26type%3D3%26theater&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=2e73a61c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=828452537517225&amp;set=a.127929567569529&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">吳文遠在蘋果日報以登頭版全版攪笑廣告的方式回應我，我要感謝他</span>，因為有兩個作用：一是引起更多人注意。今後廣告商的老闆，或者老闆的老闆就不能說不知道自己的廣告費投向蘋果日報了。二是如果外國傳媒報道吳文遠這個動作，哪即使在外國的讀者和廣告商，包括外國的大藥廠、地產商和其他供應商，都可以上我Facebook看看照片，用西方的標準，就知道怎樣做了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請大家廣傳，請吳文遠繼續宣傳，下次最好用英文再登一次。<br />\n<br />\n那些廣告商在蘋果登廣告，我會繼續廣而告之。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地而家唔驚你當你冇料到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捐左錢諗住睇人嬲嬲豬班傻仔而家覺得點?"},{"pid":"192b1d7cf76635b1d1ce5fc4bb588a9c988022aa","tid":1096723,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"以689副仆街格 一定有秋後算帳"},{"pid":"fcd68cb2f980250c6e8c1c18628938045743e76b","tid":1096723,"uid":122896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:20:38.000Z","msg":"小學雞遊戲，留返d錢幫忙打官司好過啦"},{"pid":"81544eb5cd98569205be5182f665f3eb09dd4d40","tid":1096723,"uid":106426,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb9d65928c16beaed4987d630feab4ebcc110a46","tid":1096723,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/08/102435_87983930b43295dd94f0788ba7af347f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F08%2F102435_87983930b43295dd94f0788ba7af347f.png&h=e31b0828&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8aab30ada966aaf7e07e98d0303bcb3976c69dd7","tid":1096723,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:57:35.000Z","msg":"梁振英<br />\n3小時<br />\n吳文遠和蘋果日報有沒有違反公司條例？<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠今天在蘋果日報登的全版廣告，左上角標明「贊助刋登」的是「香港人忍耐力有限公司」。<br />\n<br />\n有法律界人士經查冊後質疑：「香港人忍耐力有限公司」有沒有在香港或海外登記註冊？有沒有權用「有限公司」的聲稱？如果沒有，就觸犯了公司條例（香港法例第622章）第896節。再者，蘋果日報在接受這份廣告的時候，廣告商是否真的是「香港人忍耐力有限公司」？當中有沒有瞞騙或串謀行為？<br />\n<br />\n請吳文遠和蘋果日報澄清。<br />\n<br />\n想撚狗點知俾人撚返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cd1067b8a8dc6eb003a59d7d86702f8877cd4a","tid":1096723,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"查下發起個個同蘋果有冇關係先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131f8500c4ee43b147fb557ec8d6adee9006a567","tid":1096723,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"00cd1067b8a8dc6eb003a59d7d86702f8877cd4a","tid":1096723,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"查下發起個個同蘋果有冇關係先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:29:17.000Z","msg":"使撚查咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n社民連班金主咪蘋果囉，今次夾錢蘋果登廣告咪左手交右手"},{"pid":"f2366a0204a4790f5aafcc2f03bb2a69842c18d8","tid":1096723,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎D錢咪又係用黎支持民主運動,仲可以撚倒689,值wo"},{"pid":"53d94886627540e640e049d3e5a28a7fce11a158","tid":1096723,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"699314ebec3eef7db63c226d5d8cb79e18618251","tid":1096723,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2366a0204a4790f5aafcc2f03bb2a69842c18d8","tid":1096723,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎D錢咪又係用黎支持民主運動,仲可以撚倒689,值wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:32:50.000Z","msg":"你邊到睇到係&ldquo;撚倒689&rdquo;？<br />\n佢叫你登多幾篇喎"}]}